---
title: American-Style Black Bean Chilli with Cucumber Salad, Corn Chips & Yoghurt
description: Spice up dinner time with a black bean chilli, all the punchy flavours without the heat. We suggest grabbing a corn chip and
piling up a helping of saucy beans and yoghurt. Chase it down with a cucumber salad, for that fresh kick every chilli bowl needs.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
